  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">100만원 계좌 = 100억원 계좌</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">둘 다 '1표'로 집계</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ 군중 심리를 재는 도구</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">돈을 센다 (명목가치)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">펀딩비 · 미결제약정</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Notional-weighted</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">포지션 크기 × 가격으로</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">정산·집계</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ 청산 리스크를 재는 도구</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">예: 소액 롱 10계좌 vs 대형 숏 1계좌</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">계좌 기준 → 10:1, 롱 압도적 우위</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">자본 기준 → 순숏 우위 가능</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">어긋남은 오류가 아니라, 서로 다른 질문에 대한 서로 다른 답이다</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="en">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">The Three Metrics Measure Different Units</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Same market, different questions</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Counts people (accounts)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Long/Short Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">A $700 account = a $7M account</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Both count as one "vote"</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ A crowd-sentiment tool</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Counts money (notional)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Funding Rate · Open Interest</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Notional-weighted</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Settled by position size</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">times price</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ A liquidation-risk tool</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Ex: 10 small long accounts vs 1 large short account</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">By account &#8594; 10:1, heavily long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">By capital &#8594; could be net short</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">The mismatch isn't an error — it's two answers to two different questions</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="ja">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">三つの指標は異なる単位を測る</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">同じ市場、違う問い</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">人を数える(口座数)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">ロングショート比率</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">10万円口座 = 10億円口座</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">どちらも「1票」として集計</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; 群集心理を測る道具</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">金を数える(名目価値)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">ファンディングレート・建玉</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Notional-weighted</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">ポジションサイズ×価格で</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">清算・集計</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; 清算リスクを測る道具</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">例: 少額ロング10口座 vs 大口ショート1口座</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">口座基準 &#8594; 10:1、ロング優勢</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">資本基準 &#8594; 純ショート優勢の可能性</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">食い違いはエラーではなく、違う問いへの違う答えである</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="es">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Los Tres Indicadores Miden Unidades Distintas</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">El mismo mercado, preguntas distintas</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Cuenta personas (cuentas)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Ratio Long/Short</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Cuenta de $700 = cuenta de $7M</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Ambas cuentan como un "voto"</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Herramienta de sentimiento</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Cuenta dinero (nocional)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Financiación · Interés Abierto</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Ponderado por nocional</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Liquidado por tamaño</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">de posición × precio</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Herramienta de riesgo</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Ej: 10 cuentas largas pequeñas vs 1 corta grande</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Por cuenta &#8594; 10:1, largo dominante</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Por capital &#8594; podría ser neto corto</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">El desajuste no es un error: son dos respuestas a preguntas distintas</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="de">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Die Drei Kennzahlen Messen Unterschiedliche Einheiten</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Gleicher Markt, andere Fragen</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Zählt Menschen (Konten)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Long/Short-Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">700-$-Konto = 7-Mio.-$-Konto</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Beide zählen als eine „Stimme"</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Stimmungs-Werkzeug</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Zählt Geld (Nominalwert)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Funding Rate · Open Interest</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Kapitalgewichtet</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Abgerechnet nach Größe</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">mal Preis</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Liquidationsrisiko-Werkzeug</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Bsp: 10 kleine Long-Konten vs. 1 großes Short-Konto</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Nach Konto &#8594; 10:1, klar long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Nach Kapital &#8594; evtl. netto short</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Die Diskrepanz ist kein Fehler — es sind zwei Antworten auf zwei Fragen</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="fr">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Les Trois Indicateurs Mesurent des Unités Différentes</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Même marché, questions différentes</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Compte des personnes (comptes)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Ratio Long/Short</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Compte de 700$ = compte de 7M$</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Les deux comptent pour une « voix »</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Outil de sentiment</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Compte de l'argent (nominal)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Funding · Open Interest</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Pondéré par le nominal</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Réglé selon taille</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">de position × prix</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Outil de risque de liquidation</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Ex : 10 petits comptes long vs 1 gros compte short</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Par compte &#8594; 10:1, très long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Par capital &#8594; possiblement net short</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Le décalage n'est pas une erreur : deux réponses à deux questions</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="pt">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Os Três Indicadores Medem Unidades Diferentes</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Mesmo mercado, perguntas diferentes</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Conta pessoas (contas)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Índice Long/Short</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Conta de US$700 = de US$7M</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Ambas contam como um "voto"</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Ferramenta de sentimento</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Conta dinheiro (nocional)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Funding · Open Interest</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Ponderado por nocional</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Liquidado por tamanho</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">da posição × preço</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Ferramenta de risco</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Ex: 10 contas long pequenas vs 1 short grande</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Por conta &#8594; 10:1, dominância long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Por capital &#8594; pode ser net short</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">O desalinhamento não é erro: são duas respostas a perguntas diferentes</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="tr">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Üç Gösterge Farklı Birimleri Ölçer</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Aynı piyasa, farklı sorular</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">İnsan sayar (hesap)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Long/Short Oranı</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">700$'lık hesap = 7M$'lık hesap</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">İkisi de tek "oy" sayılır</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Duyarlılık aracı</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Para sayar (nominal)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Fonlama Oranı · Açık Pozisyon</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Nominal ağırlıklı</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Pozisyon büyüklüğü × fiyatla</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">hesaplanır</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Tasfiye riski aracı</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Örn: 10 küçük long hesap vs 1 büyük short hesap</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Hesaba göre &#8594; 10:1, ağır long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Sermayeye göre &#8594; net short olabilir</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Uyumsuzluk hata değil, iki farklı sorunun iki farklı cevabıdır</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="vi">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Ba Chỉ Báo Đo Ba Đơn Vị Khác Nhau</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Cùng thị trường, khác câu hỏi</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Đếm người (tài khoản)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Tỷ Lệ Long/Short</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">TK 700$ = TK 7 triệu $</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Đều tính là một "phiếu"</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Công cụ đo tâm lý đám đông</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Đếm tiền (danh nghĩa)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Funding Rate · Open Interest</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Tính theo giá trị danh nghĩa</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Thanh toán theo quy mô</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">vị thế × giá</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">&#8594; Công cụ đo rủi ro thanh lý</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">VD: 10 tài khoản long nhỏ vs 1 tài khoản short lớn</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Theo tài khoản &#8594; 10:1, nghiêng long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Theo vốn &#8594; có thể net short</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Sự lệch pha không phải lỗi — mà là hai câu trả lời cho hai câu hỏi khác nhau</text>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="id">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">The Three Metrics Measure Different Units</text>
  <text x="20" y="52" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Same market, different questions</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="40" y="100" fill="#f87171" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Counts people (accounts)</text>
  <text x="40" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Long/Short Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Global Account Ratio</text>
  <text x="40" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">A $700 account = a $7M account</text>
  <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Both count as one "vote"</text>
  <text x="40" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ A crowd-sentiment tool</text>
  <rect x="370" y="72" width="310" height="180" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="390" y="100" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Counts money (notional)</text>
  <text x="390" y="130" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="600" font-family="sans-serif">Funding Rate · Open Interest</text>
  <text x="390" y="152" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Notional-weighted</text>
  <text x="390" y="182" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">Settled by position size</text>
  <text x="390" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12.5" font-family="sans-serif">times price</text>
  <text x="390" y="230" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">→ A liquidation-risk tool</text>
  <text x="20" y="278" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13.5" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Ex: 10 small long accounts vs 1 large short account</text>
  <rect x="20" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#27191b"/>
  <text x="40" y="320" fill="#fca5a5" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">By account &#8594; 10:1, heavily long</text>
  <rect x="370" y="294" width="310" height="42" rx="6" fill="#182234"/>
  <text x="390" y="320" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">By capital &#8594; could be net short</text>
  <text x="350" y="378" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">The mismatch isn't an error — it's two answers to two different questions</text>
</svg>
</div>
